400g pizza dough from 250g flour
form into a log
rest 1 hour
roll to 13x9
top all but 13x3 with
 - garlic oil
 - parsley or basil
 - 150 g meat: pepperoni, salami, ham, cooked minced steak,
 - 150g cheese: mozzarella, parmesan, provolone
fold dough sides over meat
roll into 13" long log
can be kept in the fridge for several hours
rest 15 minutes 
cut slits on top
top with parmesan 
place on a sheet pan 
bake 35 minutes @400 to 200 internal
serve with marinara sauce
